title: SCI-FI FLYBY SFX PACK
description: A pack of high quality, professionally produced, and accurately modeled Doppler effect flyby sounds for your game!
longDescription:
Video Preview: http://bit.ly/FlybyVideoPreview

Audio Preview: http://bit.ly/FlybyAudioPreview


Free samples of this pack here: http://bit.ly/FlybyFreePack


A pack of high quality, professionally produced spacecraft flyby sound effects. Sci-Fi Flyby SFX Pack will give your game the edge you are looking for. Add realistic and accurately modeled Doppler effects to your spaceships. Find the exact sound you need with the hundreds of audio files included. Intensify your game’s experience. Give it the sound it deserves!


Discover:

  • High quality sounds crafted from industry leading synths
  • 5 Sci-Fi vehicles
  • 6 flyby patterns with 3 different Doppler lengths
  • Flybys have been captured in increments of 100MPH up to 700MPH
  • Vehicles include 3 different engine start ups, full RPM loop, and blast off

*The 3 engine start up files blend seamlessly into the full RPM file* 

  • 131 sound files for each vehicle
  • Over 470MB of HQ audio content


Find the complete asset list here: http://bit.ly/FlybyAssetList
technicalDetails:
Total Audio Files: 671

Total Cues: 671

Total Minutes of Audio: 46 minutes 25 seconds

Format: 44.1 kHz & 16 bit

Does the audio Loop? Some yes and some no

Number of Sound FX: 671

Target Platform: All

Documentation Included: Asset list only (see link above)

Important/Additional Notes: No
